export class SidebarComponent {

  userName = 'Jane Doe';

  isOpen = true;


  toggleSidebar() {

    this.isOpen = !this.isOpen;

  }


  getUserInitials(): string {

    return this.userName

      .split(' ')

      .map((n) => n[0])

      .join('');

  }

}
